  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/52717e2d0772a90d4459590ffc5b5763.avif?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Azoove is a co-op card roguelike about overcoming limited communication on an ill-fated save-the-world road trip to seal a cursed book.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive together with online multiplayer, playing cards to <strong>manage resources</strong>, mitigating each day's new dangers (<strong>Misfortunes</strong>)<strong> </strong>as you trek further through the Azoove desert.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During one phase of each round, communication with allies is limited to exchanging cards without revealing your hand. You must learn to trust in your teammates — or die trying.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WILL YOU MAKE IT IN TIME? OR WILL YOU BE LOST TO THE SANDS OF AZOOVE?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/a4e547bced417c2ed2f2b8739c887b81.avif?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/53f9221040acff6b5f28fd5db966ad06.poster.avif?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/53f9221040acff6b5f28fd5db966ad06.webm?t=1759868843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/53f9221040acff6b5f28fd5db966ad06.mp4?t=1759868843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Mechanic: Overcoming Limited Communications</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collaborate Silently!</strong> As the Heroes fan out in search of <strong>Opportunity Cards</strong>, players are not allowed to discuss their hand. You must instead deduce the best move from what little planning and information you have.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exchange Opportunity Cards</strong> strategically to share information and optimize the use of dwindling resources. Create unique communication patterns that help interpret the meaning behind traded cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game will not</i> force <i>silence on you. You are expected to be using your own communication software (such as Discord) and follow the rules (or don't — we can't stop you but we promise it is more fun this way)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/2b1acbdf930d395c69d64d2493a446b1.poster.avif?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/2b1acbdf930d395c69d64d2493a446b1.webm?t=1759868843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/2b1acbdf930d395c69d64d2493a446b1.mp4?t=1759868843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/93cadc64433f92123c969007421b1012.webp?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as 4 heroes with their unique powers and cards:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oriana, the Ranger</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sage, the Forager</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auri, the Bard</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rin, the Guardian</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/19bdb64563317895673d7c5779118060.avif?t=1759868843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras_big/19bdb64563317895673d7c5779118060.avif?t=1759868843 width=800 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/93cadc64433f92123c969007421b1012.webp?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A lifetime past</strong>, Farloon's founder saved his people with a stolen book of secrets. Now, with his death, the payment comes due - the souls of your city. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>returning the grimoire</strong> to its rightful wardens may divert Farloon's fate - but a deadly desert lies between you and your city's salvation. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CAN YOU RETURN THE TOME IN TIME? HOW WILL YOU SURVIVE ARID AZOOVE?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/4f90789c7635f537fa230848f564369d.avif?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/93cadc64433f92123c969007421b1012.webp?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Replayability and Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tinker with <strong>Trinkets</strong>: items that grant passive abilities that strengthen and steer each expedition in exciting new ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you overcome Azoove's normal challenges, add <strong>additional rules</strong> to complicate and <strong>challenge</strong> veteran players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435450/extras/483bdf637dae29138ab81eca293d2c6f.webp?t=1759868843\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p>",
